name: Green nature and polluted black river

metadata.name: Dragon Kingkong game
metadata.description: Dragons and dragon characters smile friendly, but they are pink monsters that symbolize human greed and selfishness. Garbage thrown away while we were wearing clothes was dumped into the river without a purifier, polluting the river black. I hope that the world will work together to restore nature to health by fighting the silly smiling dragon that symbolizes selfishness and folly in our hearts to protect and restore the planet.
